<template><div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl"><h1>Messages</h1><p class="lead">Messages are what conversations are made of in Protocol â€” they are the basic building blocks of your conversations with your Protocol contacts. On this page, we'll dive into the different message endpoints you can use to manage messages programmatically.</p><h2>The message model</h2><p>The message model contains all the information about the messages and attachments you send to your contacts and groups.</p><h3>Properties</h3><div class="space-y-3"><div class="border border-zinc-900/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3"><div class="font-semibold text-sm"><code>id</code> <span class="text-zinc-500">string</span></div><p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 m-0">Unique identifier for the message.</p></div><div class="border border-zinc-900/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3"><div class="font-semibold text-sm"><code>conversation_id</code> <span class="text-zinc-500">string</span></div><p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 m-0">Unique identifier for the conversation the message belongs to.</p></div><div class="border border-zinc-900/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3"><div class="font-semibold text-sm"><code>message</code> <span class="text-zinc-500">string</span></div><p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 m-0">The message content.</p></div><div class="border border-zinc-900/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3"><div class="font-semibold text-sm"><code>created_at</code> <span class="text-zinc-500">timestamp</span></div><p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 m-0">Timestamp of when the message was created.</p></div></div><h2>List all messages</h2><p>This endpoint allows you to retrieve a paginated list of all your messages. By default, a maximum of ten messages are shown per page.</p><div class="bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-zinc-950 rounded-lg p-4 my-6 overflow-x-auto"><div class="text-xs text-zinc-400 mb-2">GET /v1/messages</div><pre class="text-zinc-200 m-0"><code>curl -G https://api.protocol.chat/v1/messages \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer {token}" \
  -d limit=10</code></pre></div></div></template>
